<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-2173] Move FrameBuffer creation to a factory method for cusomization</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2173</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Apache Accumulo and (at least) Apache Cassandra try to provide the client address in the server&apos;s executing thread, primarily for debugging/logging purposes.  If the construction of FrameBuffer objects was done in a FactoryMethod that we could override, it would help tremendously.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
